<item>
            <title>[LU-5502] High level description of three modules and relationships</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5502</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As part of the Code Documentation project for OpenSFS, we have agreed to do three more files.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Add a high level description of the subsystem to the .c file that implements the module_init() function.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Answer the question &quot;What does this module do?&quot;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Explain where it sits in the layered object/device model,&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;what services it provides to adjacent layers,&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;what type of processing it does on incoming and outgoing requests,&lt;br/&gt;
etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;SCOPE:&lt;br/&gt;
 + LOD&lt;br/&gt;
 + OSP&lt;br/&gt;
 + OFD&lt;/p&gt;</description>
